1
00:00:00,728 --> 00:00:01,192
Hope.
霍普

2
00:00:01,836  --> 00:00:03,392
Look at me.
看着我

3
00:00:04,368 --> 00:00:05,396
I'm expendable.
他可以牺牲我

4
00:00:06,156  --> 00:00:08,180
That's why I'm here.
这就是我在这儿的原因

5
00:00:08,828  --> 00:00:11,476
You must've realized that by now.
你现在一定明白了吧

6
00:00:11,608  --> 00:00:14,540
I mean, that's why I'm in the suit and you're not.
这就是为什么是我来穿战衣而不是你

7
00:00:15,676  --> 00:00:18,560
He'd rather lose this fight than lose you.
他宁愿输掉这一战也不愿失去你

8
00:00:20,336 --> 00:00:21,152
anyway.
算了吧

9
00:00:22,416 --> 00:00:25,160
You know, I didn't know you had a daughter,
当时我报警的时候

10
00:00:25,544  --> 00:00:28,532
when I called the cops on you.
我并不知道你有个女儿

11
00:00:32,124 --> 00:00:33,172
What's her name?
她叫什么

12
00:00:34,232 --> 00:00:34,924
Cassie.
凯茜

13
00:00:35,900  --> 00:00:37,920
It's a pretty name.
好名字

14
00:00:40,724  --> 00:00:42,740
You have to clear your mind, Scott.
你必须清除杂念 斯科特

15
00:00:42,796 --> 00:00:44,224
You have to make your thoughts precise,
你脑海里的思路必须精准

16
00:00:44,252 --> 00:00:45,892
that's how it works.
那样才行

17
00:00:47,824 --> 00:00:48,736
Think about Cassie,
想想凯茜

18
00:00:48,768  --> 00:00:50,752
about how badly you want to see her,
想想你多么想见她

19
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:52,748
and use that to focus.
用这样来集中精神

20
00:01:01,940 --> 00:01:02,900
Open your eyes,
睁开眼睛

21
00:01:03,260 --> 00:01:05,960
and just think about what you want the ants to do.
专心去想你要让蚂蚁做什么

22
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,596
That's good.
很好